<p>The whole atmosphere inside the company is just amazing. It is carefully build by our positive efforts and based on six main rocks:<br/>•	Creative and proactive team <br/>•	Development as a workstyle<br/>•	Comfortable office space, which inspires and motivates<br/>•	Health care program<br/>•	Sport activities and gaming in everyday life<br/>•	Rich event calendar</p>
