<p>Its aim is to tackle crippling challenges of medical data collection such as poor response rates, low patient engagement, high cost or limited abilities to customize care based on a personal information. Our medical data collection platform is meant to fulfill both needs and dreams of clinicians, providers, and researchers, enabling to carefully collect and thoroughly patient health information.</p>
<p>Tonic is now used by healthcare providers, including the TOP-10 leading organizations in the USA.</p>
