<p>Про нашу команду і життя компанії :)</p>
<p><a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9DHMILntnLpY-r8TNp-Kbg" target="_blank">www.youtube.com/…​/UC9DHMILntnLpY-r8TNp-Kbg</a><br/><a href="https://www.facebook.com/LuckyLabsCompany" target="_blank">www.facebook.com/LuckyLabsCompany</a><br/><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/lucky-labs" target="_blank">www.linkedin.com/company/lucky-labs</a><br/>#worknsmile</p></div>', null, 'static/images/brand/lucky-labs.png', 'http://lucky-labs.com/', null, 0, 0, 0, '2017-04-15 13:08:03.245941', 'Мальта, Кипр, Киев, Одесса, Москва (Россия)', null, null);
INSERT INTO parseville_company (id, name, alias, description, short_text, logo, url, event_url, show, show_on_main, has_parser, date, extra, news_url, vacancy_url) VALUES (42, 'Grossum', 'grossum', '<div><p><b>Grossum: Developing a Better Future</b></p>
<p>Join the family! We are a pack of people who are passionate about coding, love to work alongside professionals (since we are pros ourselves) and we’re looking for good-natured, proactive, and initiative developers to join us. </p>
<p>We work with web &amp; mobile (native &amp; cross-platform) development and everything that comes with it. We have experience with developing complex high-load websites on Symfony as well as mobile apps with deep architecture and unique features (such as a UV-like camera). We also provide DevOps and UI/UX design services that are important parts of a successful project. Check out our <a href="http://www.grossum.com/services" target="_blank">services</a> and <a href="http://www.grossum.com/expertise" target="_blank">expertise</a>.</p>
<p>We also organize Symfony Cafe Kyiv — a place where PHP / Symfony geeks meet and share knowledge. We participate in hackathons and the EU Web Challenge. Our developers share their knowledge at events like SymfonyCamp, #SymfonyCafeKyiv, PHP Frameworks Day and other.</p>
<p><b>What do you get as a part of our family?<b></b></b></p>
<ul><li>Do what you love to do (you love coding, right?) and get paid for it! </li><li>Our coffee, cookies and candy have been tested by our best QA specialists </li><li>You can go on vacation and still get paid! (Limited days offer, however)</li><li>English Speaking Club and English “Alias” game — enjoy the language practice</li><li>We don’t like it when someone gets sick, but we are all human. Therefore, if something happens to you, you can take a paid sick leave. (We’ll make you a bowl of chicken soup to make you feel better, too) </li><li>Extra days off on public holidays — it’s always good to sleep in, right? </li><li>We are a growing company and there are many opportunities to grow and develop </li></ul>
<p>Be a part of the change!</p>
<p><b>You can also <a href="http://www.facebook.com/GrossumSoft" target="_blank">follow us</a> on Facebook!</b></p></div>', null, 'static/images/brand/grossum.png', 'http://www.grossum.com/', null, 0, 0, 0, '2017-04-15 13:08:05.101462', 'Киев', null, null);
