<p>Migon Mobile team is high-skilled in writing software that maximize device potential for Apple, Android and Windows mobile devices.</p>
<p>Our Web-team are professionals in e-commerce websites development, using our own high performance and SEO-friendly framework.</p></div>', null, '', 'http://migonsoftware.com/', null, 0, 0, 0, '2017-04-15 13:11:35.167584', 'Киев', null, null);